description: It’s been over a decade since the last time we set out as Link in a new 2D Legend of Zelda game (I refuse to acknowledge the existence of TriForce Heroes), but the next installment in the top down flavor of the franchise will actually have us playing as the titular princess! Here’s everything you need to know about The Legend of Zelda: Echoes of Wisdom.
title: Legend Of Zelda: Echoes Of Wisdom Everything To Know

description:

title: PlayStation State of Play September 2024 Livestream
